  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375760/extras/422f98fba61c724f9b50f3087b4bdd6e.avif?t=1753484674\" width=640 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>\"Tropicalia: a Brazilian Game\"</i></strong> is a tropical RPG based on Tupi-Guarani mythology. The first ever <strong><i>bRPG</i></strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375760/extras/3425ac83b9bfae737bfa6c3418d9d961.poster.avif?t=1753484674\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375760/extras/3425ac83b9bfae737bfa6c3418d9d961.webm?t=1753484674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375760/extras/3425ac83b9bfae737bfa6c3418d9d961.mp4?t=1753484674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is a <strong>love letter to Super Nintendo RPGs</strong>, but set in an ancient South America – like you've never seen before!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s a classic turn-based RPG, but designed for a modern audience. So here’s what you’ll find:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interactive battle system (Quick-Time Events);</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple map exploration abilities;</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Playground Mode with no battles, just to enjoy the story;</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375760/extras/566825faa6e9b25ec322b20887d39985.poster.avif?t=1753484674\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375760/extras/566825faa6e9b25ec322b20887d39985.webm?t=1753484674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375760/extras/566825faa6e9b25ec322b20887d39985.mp4?t=1753484674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will play as <strong>Kaique</strong>, a brave Guarani warrior whose girlfriend, <strong>Kerana</strong>, is kidnapped by an evil god named <strong>Tau</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tropicalia is all about gameplay. Dialogue is here to build a unique atmosphere. After all, it’s not every day you get to eat your enemies’ flesh (as a sign of respect)!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect materials to craft new items. Grind through fast-paced battles. Test your strategy against challenging bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hunt, fish, swim, dive, jump, and explore the jungle!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Here you WON’T find Dragons and Elves. But you will face <strong>Curupiras</strong> and <strong>Boitatas</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Are You Ready for This Tropical Adventure?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375760/extras/422f98fba61c724f9b50f3087b4bdd6e.avif?t=1753484674\" width=640 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>\"Tropicalia: a Brazilian Game\"</i></strong> is a tropical RPG based on Tupi-Guarani mythology. The first ever <strong><i>bRPG</i></strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375760/extras/3425ac83b9bfae737bfa6c3418d9d961.poster.avif?t=1753484674\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375760/extras/3425ac83b9bfae737bfa6c3418d9d961.webm?t=1753484674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375760/extras/3425ac83b9bfae737bfa6c3418d9d961.mp4?t=1753484674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is a <strong>love letter to Super Nintendo RPGs</strong>, but set in an ancient South America – like you've never seen before!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s a classic turn-based RPG, but designed for a modern audience. So here’s what you’ll find:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interactive battle system (Quick-Time Events);</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple map exploration abilities;</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Playground Mode with no battles, just to enjoy the story;</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375760/extras/566825faa6e9b25ec322b20887d39985.poster.avif?t=1753484674\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375760/extras/566825faa6e9b25ec322b20887d39985.webm?t=1753484674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375760/extras/566825faa6e9b25ec322b20887d39985.mp4?t=1753484674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will play as <strong>Kaique</strong>, a brave Guarani warrior whose girlfriend, <strong>Kerana</strong>, is kidnapped by an evil god named <strong>Tau</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tropicalia is all about gameplay. Dialogue is here to build a unique atmosphere. After all, it’s not every day you get to eat your enemies’ flesh (as a sign of respect)!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect materials to craft new items. Grind through fast-paced battles. Test your strategy against challenging bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hunt, fish, swim, dive, jump, and explore the jungle!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Here you WON’T find Dragons and Elves. But you will face <strong>Curupiras</strong> and <strong>Boitatas</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Are You Ready for This Tropical Adventure?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
